#           2. [x] Colors (Specific)                                                                      #
#           3. [x] Night Colors (Specific)                                                                #
#           4. Application Appearance Style (Specific)                                                    #
#           5. Plasma Appearance Style (Specific)                                                         #
#           6. Windows Decoration Elements (Specific)                                                     #
#           7. Icons                                                                                      #
#           8. Cursors                                                                                    #
#           9. [x] System Sounds (Specific)                                                               #
#          10. [x] Weclome Screen (Specific)                                                              #
#          11. Login Screen (SDDM)                                                                        #
#          12. Boot Screen                                                                                #
#                                                                                                         #
# Among them, [x] indicates "not considered".                                                             #
#             (Specific) means that it may be specific to the KDE Plasma.                                 #
